oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Holiday Motel, Athens, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color photograph of the pool at the Holiday Motel in Athens, Tennessee. Image shows two people lounging poolside and motel buildings are visible in the background. Features a divided back with narrative and handwritten correspondence on reverse. November 9, 1971 postmark.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Motels; Swimming pools; People; Automobiles
